WEBVTT

00:00:01.142 --> 00:00:03.658
I need to make a confession
at the outset here.

00:00:03.682 --> 00:00:08.435
A little over 20 years ago,
I did something that I regret,

00:00:09.511 --> 00:00:12.182
something that I'm not
particularly proud of.

00:00:12.881 --> 00:00:16.256
Something that, in many ways,
I wish no one would ever know,

00:00:16.280 --> 00:00:19.539
but here I feel kind of obliged to reveal.

00:00:19.563 --> 00:00:20.583
(Laughter)

00:00:21.840 --> 00:00:23.864
In the late 1980s,

00:00:23.888 --> 00:00:27.283
in a moment of youthful indiscretion,

00:00:27.307 --> 00:00:28.808
I went to law school.

00:00:28.832 --> 00:00:30.770
(Laughter)